296
00:19:13,190 --> 00:19:14,349
Kamu

297
00:19:15,990 --> 00:19:17,220
sangat cantik.

298
00:19:19,289 --> 00:19:20,730
Karena ini kali pertamaku,

299
00:19:20,730 --> 00:19:23,160
