Kenapa ke sini sepagi ini?

310
00:19:59,630 --> 00:20:01,170
Aku hanya akan duduk di sini sebentar.

311
00:20:02,799 --> 00:20:03,799
Mau minum kopi?

312
00:20:04,569 --> 00:20:05,769
Kamu tidak minum kopi.

313
00:20:05,900 --> 00:20:07,769
Aku membelinya karena kupikir Anda mungkin datang.

314
00:20:10,980 --> 00:20:12,009
Silakan.

315
00:20:13,410 --> 00:20:14,480
Terima kasih.

316
00:20:16,319 --> 00:20:17,319
Anda sudah

317
