343
00:21:50,039 --> 00:21:51,039
Ya?

344
00:21:51,240 --> 00:21:52,440
Tolong jangan menangis.

345
00:21:53,079 --> 00:21:54,309
Hari ini saja.

346
00:21:57,950 --> 00:21:58,950
Baik.

347
00:22:04,190 --> 00:22:05,960
Pengantin wanita datang.

348
00:22:34,589 --> 00:22:37,660
Dia benar-benar Jung Hyo?

349
00:22:37,960 --> 00:22:40,390
