00:26:20,809 --> 00:26:21,910
Aku akan mengingatnya.

411
00:26:23,480 --> 00:26:26,019
Astaga.

412
00:26:36,500 --> 00:26:37,529
Terima kasih

413
00:26:38,960 --> 00:26:40,299
